OL,3,CMoment escaping thieves drive lorry
OL,4,Cthe wrong way down motorway
OL,6,FThis is the moment police caught up
OL,7,Fwith the gang as they careered down
OL,8,Fthe M42
OL,10,FFour men have been jailed after being
OL,11,Fcaught stealing from a Cornish
OL,12,Fdistillery before driving a truck with
OL,13,Ffalse plates the wrong way down a
OL,14,Fmotorway.
OL,16,FThe gang stole more than #80,000 of
OL,17,Fpremium gin, rum and Champagne from a
OL,18,Fsite in Wadebridge in the early hours
OL,19,Fof September 8 last year.
