OL,3,CMoment escaping thieves drive lorry
OL,4,Cthe wrong way down motorway
OL,6,FThey were then spotted driving on the
OL,7,FM5 with cloned plates, leading to a
OL,8,Fpursuit that saw them drive the wrong
OL,9,Fway along the M42 before ramming a
OL,10,Fpolice car, injuring two officers.
OL,12,FA rolling road block was put in place
OL,13,Fand the lorry was stung causing the
OL,14,Ftyres to deflate.
OL,16,FOnce it had crashed, the driver and
OL,17,Fthe front passenger made off on foot,
OL,18,Fcrossing the busy lanes of the
OL,19,Fmotorway.
