OL,3,CMoment escaping thieves drive lorry
OL,4,Cthe wrong way down motorway
OL,6,FThe driver was caught shortly
OL,7,Fafterwards while the passenger was
OL,8,Farrested on the grass verge. Officers
OL,9,Fthen found three men in the back of
OL,10,Fthe lorry along with the stolen
OL,11,Falcohol.
OL,13,FThe events as they unfolded
OL,15,FDramatic footage of the chase released
OL,16,Fby West Midlands Police shows the
OL,17,Fwhite van careering along the M42,
OL,18,Fbefore exiting at junction nine.
