OL,4,Cthe wrong way down motorway
OL,6,FThe driver then attempted to rejoin
OL,7,Fthe motorway but drove along the
OL,8,Fmotorway exit slip-road, leading the
OL,9,Fvehicle into oncoming traffic.
OL,11,FA police vehicle that attempted to
OL,12,Fblock the lorry was struck, causing
OL,13,Fthe officers inside severe bruising
OL,14,Fand whiplash.
