OL,4,Cthe wrong way down motorway
OL,6,FAnother car was also struck, causing
OL,7,Fthree people minor injuries before a
OL,8,Fpolice car managed to ram the lorry
OL,9,Finto the central barrier.JThe driver
OL,10,Fof the lorry immediately made off
OL,11,Facross the busy all lanes of the
OL,12,Fmotorway but was caught a distance
OL,13,Faway.
OL,15,FThe front seat passenger was also
OL,16,Farrested on the grass verge. Inside
OL,17,Fthe back of the lorry, officers found
OL,18,Fthree men with the stolen alcohol.
