OL,6,F'The consequences could have been
OL,7,Fcatastrophic if the truck was not
OL,8,Fstopped' - police
OL,10,FAll five men have now been sentenced
OL,11,Ffor their roles in the theft and
OL,12,Fsubsequent police chase.
