OL,3,CMoment escaping thieves drive lorry
OL,4,Cthe wrong way down motorway
OL,6,FThe driver, Adam Leek, 40 of
OL,7,FBirmingham, was jailed for five years
OL,8,Fand eight months after he admitted
OL,9,Fconspiracy to commit burglary, two
OL,10,Fcounts of assaulting an emergency
OL,11,Fworker, dangerous driving, driving
OL,12,Fwhile disqualified and without
OL,13,Finsurance. He was also banned from
OL,14,Fdriving for 65 months.
OL,16,FThe front passenger, Sam Hall, 29 of
OL,17,Fno fixed address, was jailed for 31
OL,18,Fmonths for conspiracy to commit
OL,19,Fburglary and possession of a class B
OL,20,Fdrug.
