OL,3,CMoment escaping thieves drive lorry
OL,4,Cthe wrong way down motorway
OL,6,FJames Delaney, 37; Joshua Selvey, 23,
OL,7,Fand Reiss Crombie, 32, all from
OL,8,FBirmingham, were each jailed for 33,
OL,9,F28 and 28 months respectively for
OL,10,Fconspiracy to commit burglary.
OL,12,FSelvey was also convicted of
OL,13,Fpossession of a class B drug.JDelaney
OL,14,Ffailed to appear at court for a second
OL,15,Ftime and was sentenced in his absence.
OL,16,FA warrant has been issued for his
OL,17,Farrest and he is on the run.
