OL,6,FA trial at Birmingham Crown Court
OL,7,Fheard the theft had been extensively
OL,8,Fplanned and each of the gang had
OL,9,Fspecific roles.
OL,11,FThe premises and offices in Wadebridge
OL,12,Fwere ransacked, bottles of alcohol
OL,13,Fwere opened and smashed on the floor
OL,14,Fand entry points were damaged,
OL,15,Frequiring thousands of pounds of
OL,16,Frepairs.
