OL,3,CMoment escaping thieves drive lorry
OL,4,Cthe wrong way down motorway
OL,6,FSpeaking about the police pursuit,
OL,7,Finspector Sion Hathaway, from Central
OL,8,FMotorway Police Group, said: "Our
OL,9,Fofficers are highly trained at driving
OL,10,Fin unpredictable and dangerous
OL,11,Fsituations. They continually assess
OL,12,Fany pursuit to determine risk to the
OL,13,Fsubject vehicle and other road users.
OL,15,F"The driver of the lorry had only one
OL,16,Faim, which was to avoid capture, no
OL,17,Fmatter the cost to other members of
OL,18,Fthe public. We were assisted by the
OL,19,FNational Police Air Service to bring
OL,20,Fthe incident to conclusion as safely
OL,21,Fas possible.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
