OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1709407076
OL,3,CMoment escaping thieves drive lorry
OL,4,Cthe wrong way down motorway
OL,6,F"The brave actions of my staff are a
OL,7,Freminder of how police officers don't
OL,8,Fhesitate to put themselves in harm's
OL,9,Fway to protect the public. Had the
OL,10,Fofficers not taken positive action to
OL,11,Fstop this vehicle the consequences
OL,12,Fcould have been catastrophic.
OL,14,F"The serious injuries suffered by two
OL,15,Fofficers left them in severe pain and
OL,16,Fneeding lengthy treatment, which they
OL,17,Fare continuing to recover from today.
OL,18,FI applaud their actions on the day
OL,19,Fwhich no doubt prevented potential
OL,20,Finjury to members of the public."
